{"tid":1797440,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"期待彩蛋 - 陳也","createTime":"2019-12-25T12:09:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-25T12:10:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6ee9362dc72f1be5a949c5c3825c0440e7f337ca","tid":1797440,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:09:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191225/20831017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191225%2F20831017%2F&d=TvOq0m68uPCtaVYdNLQuFMdEKmWGZzYthIwftZf8Bt0%3D&h=ba07bb51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191225%2F20831017%2F&h=02d8aac6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20191225/20831017/</a><br />\n<br />\n期待彩蛋 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191225/large/1577170332_cd49.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191225%2Flarge%2F1577170332_cd49.jpg&h=6dec07a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n商場播放着老歌Last X'mas。<br />\n<br />\n去年聖誕，你還記得嗎？<br />\n<br />\n倒帶，重溫商場沒有防暴green objects，豪爽食聖誕大餐的市民，絕無諗過一年之後，大餐隨時加料落重TG和胡椒彈。去年今日，最鍾意行mall的香港人，購物大過天。一年之後，將習慣甩掉，mall中並無黃金屋，絲打巴打銀髮族快速適應，追蹤黃經、緊貼黃圈。去年的購物狂，今年轉晒型。買禮物的，黯然買了聖誕卡，送去和你寫，寫給荔枝角被拘禁不准保釋的N個手足。<br />\n<br />\n去年今日，離我們香港人，好遠啊。<br />\n<br />\n今年聖誕，白色恐懼交叉黑衣抗爭，確實是灰灰的，守護香港的路途上，凍結了，只是銀行七千萬，記住，不是人們的心。如果聖誕是真Last，最後一道聖誕福音，就是：凡活着的，都得替死去的弟兄走下去。<br />\n<br />\n1.1萬個領取9.5億補水的黑警，刻意播下怨恨的毒種，半年下來深埋本土，隨時引爆。這個聖誕，堅決謝絕大餐的人，留力復活，全民動手挖毒，還本土乾淨。三月，期待彩蛋。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"9eb625ab686168c34c52b0359e94724333e4e83d","tid":1797440,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T12:10:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">無忘承諾 並肩同行<br />\n民陣元誕大遊行</span><br />\n日期 : 1月1日 (三)<br />\n時間：14:00<br />\n地點：維園中央草坪 ==&gt; 遮打道行人專用區"}]}